Egg: Transparent/white, laid freely (
Figs 20–50
). Spherical, with conical processes ( 9 on circumference of egg). Diameter without processes 80.8 , with processes 134.0. Processes 24.7–28.5 high and 27.6–28.5 wide at the base, with slender, short, flexible distal portion (
Figs 30–44
